{"word":"Blood","slug":"blood","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Blood</b> - <b>(1)</b> Of Christ. See CHRIST JESUS<p/><b>(2) Sprinkled</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=12&verse=7'>Exo 12:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=24&verse=8'>Exo 24:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=4&verse=6'>Lev 4:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=19&verse=4'>Num 19:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=11&verse=28'>Heb 11:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=12&verse=24'>Heb 12:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=1&verse=2'>1Pe 1:2</a><p/><b>(3) Innocent,</b> Allusions to the Shedding of<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=19&verse=10'>Deu 19:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=19&verse=5'>1Sa 19:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=2&verse=31'>1Ki 2:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=21&verse=16'>2Ki 21:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=94&verse=21'>Psa 94:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=59&verse=7'>Isa 59:7</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=25&chapter=4&verse=13'>Lam 4:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=29&chapter=3&verse=19'>Joe 3:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=32&chapter=1&verse=14'>Jon 1:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27&verse=4'>Mat 27:4</a><p/><b>(4) Forbidden</b> to be eaten<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=9&verse=4'>Gen 9:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=3&verse=17'>Lev 3:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=7&verse=26'>Lev 7:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=1